Lynda FERRARI, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Joan F. O'SHEA, M.D., Defendant-Petitioner,
and
Virtual West Jersey Hospital, Defendant. C-349 September Term 2018
081713 Supreme Court of New Jersey. NOVEMBER 16, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003269-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
